Cell["\<\
1. Look at the shape of V between spikes. Is it a straight line or a curve? \
Why?

It is a\[NonBreakingSpace]curve (exponential), not a straight line. The LIF \
equation causes the membrane potential to\[NonBreakingSpace]exponentially \
approach\[NonBreakingSpace]the steady value\[NonBreakingSpace]
Vrest + RI, so the voltage rises in a curved shape until it reaches the \
threshold.

2. What happens to V after the current turns off (t > 0.4)? Describe what you \
see and explain it in
terms of the LIF equation.

The spikes stop and\[NonBreakingSpace]\|01d449decays exponentially back to \
the resting potential\[NonBreakingSpace]Vrest. This happens because when\
\[NonBreakingSpace]It = (0) the leak term in the LIF equation pulls the \
voltage back toward rest.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"cd343712-e7b0-4ce3-bcf0-3a068fc6d4e3"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Manipulate", "[", "\n", " ", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"Module", "[", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"{", 
      RowBox[{
      "vsol", ",", " ", "sc", ",", " ", "st", ",", " ", "iFunc", ",", " ", 
       "Vinf", ",", " ", "tCross"}], "}"}], ",", "\n", "\n", "  ", 
     RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
      RowBox[{
      "local", " ", "input", " ", "current", " ", "using", " ", "the", " ", 
       "slider"}], " ", "*)"}], "\n", "  ", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"iFunc", "[", 
        RowBox[{"t_", "?", "NumericQ"}], "]"}], " ", ":=", " ", 
       RowBox[{"If", "[", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
         "0.05", " ", "\[LessEqual]", " ", "t", " ", "\[LessEqual]", " ", 
          "0.4"}], ",", " ", "currentVal", ",", " ", "0.0"}], "]"}]}], ";", 
      "\n", "\n", "  ", 
      RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
       RowBox[{"solve", " ", "+", " ", 
        RowBox[{"collect", " ", "spike", " ", "times", " ", "safely"}]}], " ",
        "*)"}], "\n", "  ", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"{", 
        RowBox[{"vsol", ",", " ", "st"}], "}"}], " ", "=", "\n", "    ", 
       RowBox[{"Reap", " ", "@", " ", 
        RowBox[{"NDSolveValue", "[", "\n", "      ", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"{", "\n", "        ", 
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{"tauVal", "*", 
              RowBox[{
               RowBox[{"V", "'"}], "[", "t", "]"}]}], " ", "==", " ", 
             RowBox[{
              RowBox[{"-", 
               RowBox[{"(", 
                RowBox[{
                 RowBox[{"V", "[", "t", "]"}], " ", "-", " ", "Vrest"}], 
                ")"}]}], " ", "+", " ", 
              RowBox[{"R", "*", 
               RowBox[{"iFunc", "[", "t", "]"}]}]}]}], ",", "\n", "        ", 
            
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{"V", "[", "0", "]"}], " ", "==", " ", "Vrest"}], ",", 
            "\n", "        ", 
            RowBox[{"WhenEvent", "[", "\n", "          ", 
             RowBox[{
              RowBox[{
               RowBox[{"V", "[", "t", "]"}], " ", "\[GreaterEqual]", " ", 
               "thresh"}], ",", "\n", "          ", 
              RowBox[{"{", 
               RowBox[{
                RowBox[{
                 RowBox[{"V", "[", "t", "]"}], " ", "\[Rule]", " ", 
                 "Vreset"}], ",", " ", 
                RowBox[{"Sow", "[", "t", "]"}]}], "}"}], ",", "\n", 
              "          ", 
              
              RowBox[{"\"\<LocationMethod\>\"", " ", "\[Rule]", 
               " ", "\"\<LinearInterpolation\>\""}]}], "\n", "        ", 
             "]"}]}], "\n", "      ", "}"}], ",", "\n", "      ", "V", ",", 
          " ", 
          RowBox[{"{", 
           RowBox[{"t", ",", " ", "0", ",", " ", "0.5"}], "}"}], ",", "\n", 
          "      ", 
          RowBox[{"MaxStepSize", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", 
           RowBox[{"tauVal", "/", "50"}]}]}], "\n", "    ", "]"}]}]}], ";", 
      "\n", "\n", "  ", 
