Cell["\<\
1. At what input current does your neuron first start firing? This is related \
to the rheobase you found
with the dashboard.

My neuron first started firing at about\[NonBreakingSpace]16 nA, which \
matches the rheobase I observed earlier with the interactive dashboard.

2. Is the f\[Dash]I curve a straight line, or does it curve? What would a \
perfectly straight line mean about
how the neuron encodes stimulus intensity?

The\[NonBreakingSpace]f\[Dash]I curve is curved rather than perfectly \
straight. This means the firing rate does not increase at a perfectly \
constant rate with increasing current. A perfectly straight line would mean \
the neuron encodes stimulus intensity in a strictly\[NonBreakingSpace]linear \
way, where each increase in input current produces the same increase in \
firing rate.

3. Real neurons often show a \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]saturation\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] effect at high currents (firing rate plateaus). Does \
your LIF
model show this? Why or why not?

My\[NonBreakingSpace]LIF model does not show strong saturation at high \
currents. The firing rate keeps increasing as the input current increases \
because the model is simple and does not include biological limits like \
refractory periods or ion channel dynamics that would normally cause the \
firing rate to plateau.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"28609d8b-2b59-47c0-8618-42b4e2fdbd63"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"ClearAll", "[", 
    RowBox[{
    "V", ",", " ", "t", ",", " ", "Isine", ",", " ", "vsol", ",", " ", 
     "spikeTimes", ",", " ", "spikeCount", ",", " ", "plotV", ",", " ", 
     "plotI"}], "]"}], ";"}], "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", 
  RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
   RowBox[{"Your", " ", "LIF", " ", "parameters", " ", 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"use", " ", "yours"}], ";", " ", 
      RowBox[{
      "these", " ", "match", " ", "what", " ", "you", " ", "shared", " ", 
       "earlier"}]}], ")"}]}], " ", "*)"}]}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"tau", "    ", "=", " ", "0.020"}], ";"}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Vrest", "  ", "=", " ", 
   RowBox[{"-", "70.0"}]}], ";"}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Vthresh", "=", " ", 
   RowBox[{"-", "55.0"}]}], ";"}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Vreset", " ", "=", " ", 
   RowBox[{"-", "75.0"}]}], ";"}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"R", "      ", "=", " ", "1.0"}], ";"}], "\n", "\n", 
  RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
   RowBox[{
   "Define", " ", "a", " ", "sine", " ", "wave", " ", "input", " ", "current",
     " ", 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     RowBox[{"always", " ", "positive"}], ")"}]}], " ", "*)"}]}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"Isine", "[", 
     RowBox[{"t_", "?", "NumericQ"}], "]"}], " ", ":=", " ", 
    RowBox[{"15.0", " ", "+", " ", 
     RowBox[{"12.0", "*", 
      RowBox[{"Sin", "[", 
       RowBox[{"2", " ", "Pi", "*", "5", "*", "t"}], "]"}]}]}]}], ";"}], "\n",
   "\n", 
  RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"TODO", " ", "7"}], ":", " ", 
     RowBox[{"Run", " ", "NDSolve", " ", "with", " ", 
      RowBox[{"Isine", "[", "t", "]"}], " ", "as", " ", "input", " ", 
      "current"}]}], ",", " ", 
    RowBox[{"collect", " ", "spike", " ", "times"}]}], " ", "*)"}]}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{"vsol", ",", " ", "spikeTimes"}], "}"}], " ", "=", "\n", "  ", 
    RowBox[{"Reap", " ", "@", " ", 
     RowBox[{"NDSolveValue", "[", "\n", "    ", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"{", "\n", "      ", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"tau", "*", 
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"V", "'"}], "[", "t", "]"}]}], " ", "==", " ", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"-", 
            RowBox[{"(", 
             RowBox[{
              RowBox[{"V", "[", "t", "]"}], " ", "-", " ", "Vrest"}], ")"}]}],
            " ", "+", " ", 
           RowBox[{"R", "*", 
            RowBox[{"Isine", "[", "t", "]"}]}]}]}], ",", "\n", "      ", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"V", "[", "0", "]"}], " ", "==", " ", "Vrest"}], ",", "\n", 
         "      ", 
         RowBox[{"WhenEvent", "[", "\n", "        ", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"V", "[", "t", "]"}], " ", "\[GreaterEqual]", " ", 
            "Vthresh"}], ",", "\n", "        ", 
           RowBox[{"{", 
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{
              RowBox[{"V", "[", "t", "]"}], " ", "\[Rule]", " ", "Vreset"}], ",",
              " ", 
             RowBox[{"Sow", "[", "t", "]"}]}], "}"}], ",", "\n", "        ", 
           " ", "\[Rule]"}], " ", "\n", "      ", "]"}]}], "\n", "    ", 
        "}"}], ",", "\n", "    ", "V", ",", " ", 
       RowBox[{"{", 
        RowBox[{"t", ",", " ", "0", ",", " ", "1.0"}], "}"}], ",", "\n", 
       "    ", 
       RowBox[{"MaxStepSize", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", 
        RowBox[{"tau", "/", "50"}]}]}], "\n", "  ", "]"}]}]}], ";"}], 
  "\n"}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"spikeTimes", " ", "=", " ", 
   RowBox[{"If", "[", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"spikeTimes", " ", "===", " ", 
      RowBox[{"{", "}"}]}], ",", " ", 
     RowBox[{"{", "}"}], ",", " ", 
     RowBox[{"spikeTimes", "[", 
      RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}], "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"spikeCount", " ", "=", " ", 
    RowBox[{"Length", "[", "spikeTimes", "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n", "\n", 
  RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"TODO", " ", "8"}], ":", " ", 
    RowBox[{"Two", "-", 
     RowBox[{"panel", " ", "plot"}]}], ":", " ", 
    RowBox[{"V", 
     RowBox[{"(", "t", ")"}], " ", "and", " ", "input", " ", "current"}]}], 
   " ", "*)"}]}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"plotV", " ", "=", "\n", "  ", 
    RowBox[{"Plot", "[", "\n", "    ", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"Evaluate", "[", 
       RowBox[{"vsol", "[", "t", "]"}], "]"}], ",", "\n", "    ", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"t", ",", " ", "0", ",", " ", "1.0"}], "}"}], ",", "\n", 
      "    ", 
      RowBox[{"PlotRange", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", "All"}], ",", "\n", "    ", 
      RowBox[{"AxesLabel", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", 
       RowBox[{"{", ",", " ", "}"}]}], ",", "\n", "    ", 
      RowBox[{"PlotLabel", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", 
       RowBox[{"StringForm", "[", 
        RowBox[{",", " ", "spikeCount"}], "]"}]}], ",", "\n", "    ", 
      RowBox[{"Epilog", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", 
       RowBox[{"{", "\n", "      ", 
        RowBox[{"Red", ",", " ", "Dashed", ",", " ", 
         RowBox[{"InfiniteLine", "[", 
          RowBox[{"{", 
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"{", 
             RowBox[{"0", ",", " ", "Vthresh"}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
            RowBox[{"{", 
             RowBox[{"1", ",", " ", "Vthresh"}], "}"}]}], "}"}], "]"}], ",", 
         "\n", "      ", "Blue", ",", " ", 
         RowBox[{"PointSize", "[", "0.015", "]"}], ",", "\n", "      ", 
         RowBox[{"Point", "[", 
          RowBox[{"Transpose", "[", 
           RowBox[{"{", 
            RowBox[{"spikeTimes", ",", " ", 
             RowBox[{"ConstantArray", "[", 
              RowBox[{"Vthresh", ",", " ", "spikeCount"}], "]"}]}], "}"}], 
           "]"}], "]"}]}], "\n", "    ", "}"}]}]}], "\n", "  ", "]"}]}], 
   ";"}], "\n"}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"plotI", " ", "=", "\n", "  ", 
    RowBox[{"Plot", "[", "\n", "    ", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"Evaluate", "[", 
       RowBox[{"Isine", "[", "t", "]"}], "]"}], ",", "\n", "    ", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"t", ",", " ", "0", ",", " ", "1.0"}], "}"}], ",", "\n", 
      "    ", 
      RowBox[{"PlotRange", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", "All"}], ",", "\n", "    ", 
      RowBox[{"AxesLabel", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", 
       RowBox[{"{", 
        RowBox[{"\"\<t (s)\>\"", ",", " ", "\"\<I (nA)\>\""}], "}"}]}], ",", 
      "\n", "    ", 
      RowBox[{
      "PlotLabel", " ", "\[Rule]", 
       " ", "\"\<Input Current: 5 Hz Sine (shifted positive)\>\""}]}], "\n", 
     "  ", "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n"}], "\n", 
 RowBox[{"GraphicsColumn", "[", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"plotV", ",", " ", "plotI"}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
   RowBox[{"Spacings", " ", "\[Rule]", " ", "1"}]}], "]"}]}], "Input",Expressi\
